text: Emmelie Charlotte-Victoria de Forest (born 28 February 1993; née Emmelie Engström) is a Danish singer and songwriter. She won the Eurovision Song Contest 2013, representing Denmark with the song "Only Teardrops". Emmelie de Forest claimed she is the great granddaughter of King Edward VII. Researchers said this was not true. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Danish singers Category:Living people Category:Eurovision Song Contest winners
